  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1906400/extras/d710a9d33f42d87ac0318a161885df86.poster.avif?t=1661605749\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1906400/extras/d710a9d33f42d87ac0318a161885df86.webm?t=1661605749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1906400/extras/d710a9d33f42d87ac0318a161885df86.mp4?t=1661605749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>This is a fan game based on Touhou Project, in which the protagonist, Kedama, is just a nobody in the inferior of Gensokyo, proceeding for rescuing their friends.<br>Kedama doesn’t own any ability of remote attack but their perseverance and magic movement make themself face challenges on the way and explore the world of Gensokyo.<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Plots:</h2></strong><br>There is no ifs and buts that can stop one rescuing their friends!<br>No dialog but through the perspective of Kedama and the funny mini-animation, you can easily realize what have happened in the Gensokyo world.<br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Initial Controls:</h2></strong><br>↑ ↓ ← →: move<br>C key: attack<br>X key: jump<br>Z key: dash (no invincibility)<br>Tips:<br>1. Press F1 to make the pop-up bar come up and then click the setting where you can change the controls.<br>2. Attack combos need to be discovered. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1906400/extras/ab429564dea99af056b8ef53d8ed57bd.poster.avif?t=1661605749\" width=500 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1906400/extras/ab429564dea99af056b8ef53d8ed57bd.webm?t=1661605749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1906400/extras/ab429564dea99af056b8ef53d8ed57bd.mp4?t=1661605749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1906400/extras/f2801c758985ef70d7cb38730ad1e93d.poster.avif?t=1661605749\" width=500 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1906400/extras/f2801c758985ef70d7cb38730ad1e93d.webm?t=1661605749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1906400/extras/f2801c758985ef70d7cb38730ad1e93d.mp4?t=1661605749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Characteristics:</h2></strong><br>1. Classic 2D pixel AVG. <br>2. Easy to master.<br>3. Two different difficulty levels (EASY & HARD)for you to challenge.<br>4. Five continents separately presenting the various world of Gensokyo.<br>5. Cute animation style and funny story line, which must will make you enjoy.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1906400/extras/d710a9d33f42d87ac0318a161885df86.poster.avif?t=1661605749\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1906400/extras/d710a9d33f42d87ac0318a161885df86.webm?t=1661605749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1906400/extras/d710a9d33f42d87ac0318a161885df86.mp4?t=1661605749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>This is a fan game based on Touhou Project, in which the protagonist, Kedama, is just a nobody in the inferior of Gensokyo, proceeding for rescuing their friends.<br>Kedama doesn’t own any ability of remote attack but their perseverance and magic movement make themself face challenges on the way and explore the world of Gensokyo.<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Plots:</h2></strong><br>There is no ifs and buts that can stop one rescuing their friends!<br>No dialog but through the perspective of Kedama and the funny mini-animation, you can easily realize what have happened in the Gensokyo world.<br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Initial Controls:</h2></strong><br>↑ ↓ ← →: move<br>C key: attack<br>X key: jump<br>Z key: dash (no invincibility)<br>Tips:<br>1. Press F1 to make the pop-up bar come up and then click the setting where you can change the controls.<br>2. Attack combos need to be discovered. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1906400/extras/ab429564dea99af056b8ef53d8ed57bd.poster.avif?t=1661605749\" width=500 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1906400/extras/ab429564dea99af056b8ef53d8ed57bd.webm?t=1661605749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1906400/extras/ab429564dea99af056b8ef53d8ed57bd.mp4?t=1661605749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1906400/extras/f2801c758985ef70d7cb38730ad1e93d.poster.avif?t=1661605749\" width=500 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1906400/extras/f2801c758985ef70d7cb38730ad1e93d.webm?t=1661605749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1906400/extras/f2801c758985ef70d7cb38730ad1e93d.mp4?t=1661605749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Characteristics:</h2></strong><br>1. Classic 2D pixel AVG. <br>2. Easy to master.<br>3. Two different difficulty levels (EASY & HARD)for you to challenge.<br>4. Five continents separately presenting the various world of Gensokyo.<br>5. Cute animation style and funny story line, which must will make you enjoy.",
